PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of CAROL W. McDONALD, of St. John's, Newfoundland, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term ending December 31, 1999, in the place of Melvin Woodward, whose term has expired.
